  "topic": "Linear functions",
  "source": "sat7",
  "stem": "The function f is defined by f(x) = (1/2)(x + 6). What is the value of f(4) ?",
  "choices": ["20", "12", "10", "5"],
  "answer": "5",
  "explanation": "Substituting 4 for x gives f(4) = (1/2)(4 + 6) = (1/2)(10) = 5."
}
